query:
SELECT
    COALESCE(
        SUM(
            COMPUTE_TS_RANGE_PERCENT_OVERLAP (fuel_range, $1) * fuel_used
        ),
        0.0
    ) AS "estimate!"
FROM
    fuel_measurement_ranges
WHERE
    fuel_range && $1
    AND fiskeridir_vessel_id = $2
    AND COMPUTE_TS_RANGE_PERCENT_OVERLAP (fuel_range, $1) >= 0.5
